  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2026-03-16",
    "date": "2026-04-03T15:02:23Z",
    "text": "Grocery, Farm, and Food Worker Stabilization Grant Program Act of 2026\n\nThis bill directs the Agricultural Marketing Service (AMS) to establish a grant program to provide\u00a0farmworkers, meat processing workers, and grocery workers stabilization payments in the case of a natural disaster or other disaster. Specifically, AMS must provide funding to membership organizations or labor unions representing farmworkers, meat processing workers, and grocery workers for the payments.\u00a0"
  },
